reviewText: All inclusive has never tempted me, and I'm less tempted now after visiting the crazy Benidormians at the Solana. Still; they are a good laugh and I enjoy every minute of the episodes
Came on date given so very happy to use again

Ever since we lost Mel Harvey, they're trying too hard to mention all the characters that aren't on anymore instead of truly developing the ones that they have.  I'm a huge Benidorm fan, but I'll be re-watching Seasons 1, 2 and some of 3 instead.
Loved series 5 the best so far - loved the new characters and very funny story lines.  Enjoyed seeing a bit more of Benidorm throughout the series.
